# Leet Loaf üçû

üßë‚Äçüç≥ Your personal LeetCode bakery that kneads your solutions into a perfectly organized GitHub repository. Watch your solutions rise into a beautiful collection, complete with a fresh-baked website to showcase your work.

Syncs your LeetCode solutions with your GitHub repository, provides robust data-driven insights for interview preparation and a beautiful static site to browse through all your work -- all in one delicious tool.

## üßÇ Well Seasoned & Feature Rich

- [x] Automatic LeetCode problem definition and explanation generator
- [x] Language-agnostic support. Do you solve LeetCode problems in a variety of languages? No problem!
- [x] Cross-browser extension to catalogue and sync your completed LeetCode problems, automagically!
- [x] Auto-generated static web site to browse through your work and prepare for interviews
- [x] Concise summaries and categorization for each problem so you can quickly revise and prepare by topic
- [x] Rich data-driven insights for your solutions. Find areas of improvement or track your runtime performance metrics

## ü•ê Bakery - Static Site Generator

A beautiful gallery of your solutions alongside problem definitions & explanations.

- [x] Sift through your solutions by difficulty, tags, topics and language
- [x] Track how your solutions have improved over time with a suite of performance metrics
- [x] Identify which solutions are your weakest and find areas of improvement
- [x] Scour any solution for a given topic with a quick, fuzzy search
- [x] Collate notes, tips and diagrams with your solutions to help prepare for interviews
